<title>甘肃宕昌滑坡现场搜救工作结束 21人遇难</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E7%8E%AF%E7%90%83%E6%97%B6%E6%8A%A5+%E7%94%98%E8%82%83%E5%AE%95%E6%98%8C%E6%BB%91%E5%9D%A1%E7%8E%B0%E5%9C%BA%E6%90%9C%E6%95%91%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E7%BB%93%E6%9D%9F%2021%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%87%E9%9A%BE</link>
